OL,7,     GLauren puts her family first.
OL,8,G2000FRace Across the World: The Final
OL,9,     GAfter more than 11,000km across
OL,10,     Geight countries, the teams face
OL,11,     Gone final test of endurance as
OL,12,     Gthey race to claim victory at the
OL,13,     Gfinish line in Hatgal, Mongolia.
OL,14,G2100FRace Across the World
OL,15,     GSix months after the race, all
OL,16,     Gfive teams reunite to relive
OL,17,     Gtheir 12,000km journey from
OL,18,     GPalermo to Mongolia, with unseen
OL,19,     Gmoments and unprecedented behind-
OL,20,     Gthe-scenes access.
